description: AMUNDI EUR CORPORATE BOND UCITS ETF DR – EUR (D) seeks to replicate, as closely as possible the performance of the Bloomberg Euro Corporate Bond Index, whether the trend is rising or falling while minimizing the volatility of the di?erence between the return of the Sub-Fund and the return of the Index (the “Tracking Error”). The Sub-Fund aims to achieve a level of tracking error of the SubFund and its index that will not normally exceed 1%. For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
